Package: dcmle
Type: Package
Title: Hierarchical Models Made Easy with Data Cloning
Version: 0.2-0
Date: 2012-04-27
Author: Peter Solymos
Maintainer: Peter Solymos <solymos@ualberta.ca>
Description: S4 classes around infrastructure
  provided by the dclone package to make package 
  development with data cloning for hierarchical 
  models easy as a breeze.
License: GPL-2
Depends: methods, stats4, dclone (>= 1.7-2), rjags, 
  coda, R2WinBUGS, parallel, lattice
Suggests: snow
SystemRequirements: JAGS (>= 3.0.0)
URL: http://cran.r-project.org/package=dcmle, http://dcr.r-forge.r-project.org/
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: true
